        * Fix some outlying GM implementation bugs
        * Add test for basic GM client object instantiation
        
        0.2.3 (2015-12-12)
        ------------------
        
        * Tests now also assert the API is responding w/ good "ok" values, not just HTTP 200s.
        * Py 3.5 testing included
        
